title: O Neill encourages buy local in support of potato growers (Northern Ireland Executive)
text: ( Source : Northern Ireland Executive ) Agriculture Minister Michelle O'Neill has urged buyers, processors and retailers to 'buy local' when sourcing potatoes. ~ Friday, 9 October 2015 The Minister was speaking during a visit to Wilson Country
